divs: Sighting DetailsCleaning the mass my dog did on my backyard after tipping over and rummaging through the garbage. If interested to know, I kicked my dog for that. My nephew spotted it 1st and correctly identified the object as a weather balloon. We all looked at it with my binocular and could see the object tethered below the weather balloon. Explained to my nephew what the purposes of weather balloons. They research it in the internet. Suspect people fool themselves and will report it as a UFO in your site.
